    agent prompt's ten authoring rules):

      Rule 1 - Synthetic only (AAP Section 0.7.2 NO-PII clause):
        person     = "x_[scope]_demo_agent"  (the synthetic demo user
                     authored at ../users/sys_user_x_[scope]_demo_agent.xml;
