                 appears as the person on parties 03, 06, and 08; on
                 the assigned_agent slot of every In Progress and
                 Resolved case; and on the assigned_to slot of every
                 demo task. This pattern reflects the agent's role as
                 the primary case worker who handles end-to-end case
                 progression.

